elements.name: Add a Currency to a Pay Grade

steps.name: I navigate to the Pay Grades page
I select "Vijay Ch" from the Pay Grades table
I click on Add Currency button
I select "INR" as the currency
I enter "30000" as the Minimum Salary and "50000" as the Maximum Salary
I click on Save button
I should see Successfully Saved message
I should see "INR" listed in the currencies table for "Vijay Ch"
